bbkeys: A key-grabbing tool for Blackbox.
bbkeys:
bbkeys: bbkeys is the keygrabber for the Blackbox window manager. bbkeys
bbkeys: handles all keybindings and keyboard shortcuts for Blackbox. It
bbkeys: uses Blackbox's Image classes for rendering its look and feel, so
bbkeys: bbkeys will draw itself to match whatever Blackbox style is used. It
bbkeys: is highly configurable via the bbconf GUI utility, the included
bbkeys: bbkeysconf.pl perl script, or via hand-editing bbkeys's config file.
